# βîÄβîÄβîÄ NhαΚ≠n diαΜ΅n Roblox βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ

auto_detect_roblox() {
    echo -e "${CYAN}[*] Ρêang nhαΚ≠n diαΜ΅n Roblox...${RESET}"
    for pkg in "${ROBLOX_PACKAGES[@]}"; do
        if su -c "pm list packages 2>/dev/null" | grep -q "$pkg"; then
            ROBLOX_PKG="$pkg"
            echo -e "${GREEN}[β€™] TΟ§m thαΚΞy: ${WHITE}$ROBLOX_PKG${RESET}"
            log "NhαΚ≠n diαΜ΅n Roblox: $ROBLOX_PKG"
            sleep 1
            return
        fi
    done
    echo -e "${RED}[β€½] KhΟ¥ng tΟ§m thαΚΞy Roblox tαΜ± ΡëαΜông.${RESET}"
    echo -ne "${YELLOW}NhαΚ≠p package name thαΜß cΟ¥ng: ${RESET}"
    read -r ROBLOX_PKG
    [ -z "$ROBLOX_PKG" ] && echo -e "${RED}KhΟ¥ng cΟ≥ package, thoΟΓt.${RESET}" && exit 1
    sleep 1
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ KiαΜÉm tra process βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ

is_roblox_running() {
    su -c "pidof '$ROBLOX_PKG'" > /dev/null 2>&1 || \
    su -c "ps -A 2>/dev/null | grep -q '$ROBLOX_PKG'"
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ LαΚΞy activity Ρëang focus cαΜßa Roblox βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ

get_current_focus() {
    # TrαΚΘ vαΜ¹ dΟ≤ng mCurrentFocus / mFocusedApp tαΜΪ dumpsys window
    su -c "dumpsys window windows 2>/dev/null" \
        | grep -E "mCurrentFocus|mFocusedApp" \
        | head -2
}

is_roblox_foreground() {
    get_current_focus | grep -qi "$ROBLOX_PKG"
}

get_roblox_resumed_activity() {
    # LαΚΞy tΟΣn Activity Ρëang resumed (VD: com.roblox.client/.ActivityFoo)
    su -c "dumpsys activity activities 2>/dev/null" \
        | grep -i "mResumedActivity" \
        | grep -i "$ROBLOX_PKG" \
        | head -1 \
        | sed 's/.*{[^ ]* [^ ]* \([^ ]*\).*/\1/'
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ PhΟΓt hiαΜ΅n mΟ†n hΟ§nh Ρëen / treo βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ
# DΟΙng screencap (root) βÜ£ lαΚΞy kΟ≠ch thΤΑαΜ¦c file PNG nΟ©n
# MΟ†n Ρëen hoΟ†n toΟ†n βÜ£ file PNG rαΚΞt nhαΜè (<30KB sau nΟ©n)
# MΟ†n hΟ§nh game bΟ§nh thΤΑαΜùng βÜ£ file lαΜ¦n hΤΓn nhiαΜ¹u

check_black_screen() {
    su -c "screencap -p '$TMP_SCREEN'" > /dev/null 2>&1
    if [ ! -f "$TMP_SCREEN" ]; then
        # screencap thαΚΞt bαΚΓi, khΟ¥ng kαΚΩt luαΚ≠n
        return 1
    fi
    local fsize
    fsize=$(wc -c < "$TMP_SCREEN" 2>/dev/null || echo 999999)
    su -c "rm -f '$TMP_SCREEN'" > /dev/null 2>&1

    # NαΚΩu file PNG < 30KB thΟ§ mΟ†n hΟ§nh gαΚßn nhΤΑ Ρëen/trαΚ·ng hoΟ†n toΟ†n
    if [ "$fsize" -lt 30720 ]; then
        return 0  # lΟ† mΟ†n Ρëen
    fi
    return 1
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ PhΟΓt hiαΜ΅n trαΚΓng thΟΓi Roblox βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ
# TrαΚΘ vαΜ¹: DEAD | BACKGROUND | HOME | LOADING | GAME | BLACK | FROZEN

detect_state() {
    # 1. Process chαΚΩt?
    if ! is_roblox_running; then
        echo "DEAD"
        return
    fi

    # 2. Roblox khΟ¥ng αΜü foreground (Ρëang chαΚΓy nαΜ¹n)
    if ! is_roblox_foreground; then
        echo "BACKGROUND"
        return
    fi

    # 3. Roblox αΜü foreground βÄî lαΚΞy activity
    local activity
    activity=$(get_roblox_resumed_activity)

    # 4. KiαΜÉm tra mΟ†n Ρëen (chαΜâ khi cαΚßn, tαΜën 1-2s)
    if check_black_screen; then
        echo "BLACK"
        return
    fi

    # 5. PhΟΔn tΟ≠ch tΟΣn activity
    # Activity Home/Lobby Roblox thΤΑαΜùng chαΜ©a cΟΓc tαΜΪ khoΟΓ sau:
    if echo "$activity" | grep -qiE \
        "MainActivity|AppShell|HomeActivity|SplashActivity|LoginActivity|\
         StartupActivity|LaunchActivity|BootActivity|Hub|Portal|LandingActivity"; then
        echo "HOME"
        return
    fi

    # 6. NαΚΩu activity giαΜëng activity game ΡëΟΘ biαΚΩt βÜ£ IN GAME
    if [ -n "$LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY" ] && [ "$activity" = "$LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY" ]; then
        echo "GAME"
        return
    fi

    # 7. Activity khΟ¥ng rΟΒ βÜ£ cΟ≥ thαΜÉ Ρëang loading hoαΚΖc game
    # NαΚΩu chΤΑa tαΜΪng vΟ†o game βÜ£ LOADING
    if [ "$FIRST_JOIN_DONE" = false ]; then
        echo "LOADING"
        return
    fi

    # 8. Activity thay ΡëαΜïi so vαΜ¦i game activity ΡëΟΘ biαΚΩt βÜ£ vαΜ¹ HOME/kαΚΙt
    if [ -n "$LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY" ] && [ "$activity" != "$LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY" ]; then
        echo "HOME"
        return
    fi

    # 9. MαΚΖc ΡëαΜ΄nh: coi lΟ† Ρëang loading
    echo "LOADING"
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ HΟ†nh ΡëαΜông rejoin βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ

send_join_intent() {
    # GαΜ≠i deep link vΟ†o game, KHΟîNG kill Roblox nαΚΩu Ρëang chαΚΓy
    su -c "am start -a android.intent.action.VIEW \
        -d 'roblox://placeId=${PLACE_ID}' \
        '${ROBLOX_PKG}'" > /dev/null 2>&1

    if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then
        # Fallback: am start -p rαΜ™i gαΜ≠i intent
        su -c "am start -p '${ROBLOX_PKG}'" > /dev/null 2>&1
        sleep 2
        su -c "am start -a android.intent.action.VIEW \
            -d 'roblox://placeId=${PLACE_ID}'" > /dev/null 2>&1
    fi
}

force_stop_and_rejoin() {
    echo -e "${YELLOW}  βÜ£ Force stop Roblox...${RESET}"
    su -c "am force-stop '${ROBLOX_PKG}'" > /dev/null 2>&1
    sleep 3
    FIRST_JOIN_DONE=false
    LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY=""
    send_join_intent
}

do_rejoin() {
    local reason="$1"
    REJOIN_COUNT=$((REJOIN_COUNT + 1))
    log "=== REJOIN #${REJOIN_COUNT} | LΟΫ do: ${reason} | PlaceID=${PLACE_ID} ==="
    echo -e "${MAGENTA}[REJOIN #${REJOIN_COUNT}] LΟΫ do: ${reason}${RESET}"
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ VΟ£NG LαΚΕP CHΟçNH βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ

start_rejoin_loop() {
    if [ -z "$PLACE_ID" ]; then
        echo -e "${RED}[!] ChΤΑa thiαΚΩt lαΚ≠p Place ID!${RESET}"; sleep 2; return
    fi
    if [ -z "$ROBLOX_PKG" ]; then
        echo -e "${RED}[!] ChΤΑa nhαΚ≠n diαΜ΅n package Roblox!${RESET}"; sleep 2; return
    fi

    IS_RUNNING=true
    REJOIN_COUNT=0
    FIRST_JOIN_DONE=false
    LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY=""
    LAST_STATE=""
    STATE_SINCE=$(now)

    echo ""
    echo -e "${GREEN}${BOLD}[β€™] BαΚ·t ΡëαΚßu Auto Rejoin Loop!${RESET}"
    echo -e "  Place ID : ${CYAN}${PLACE_ID}${RESET}"
    echo -e "  Package  : ${CYAN}${ROBLOX_PKG}${RESET}"
    echo -e "  KiαΜÉm tra : mαΜ½i ${CYAN}${DELAY_CHECK}s${RESET}"
    echo -e "${YELLOW}  NhαΚΞn Ctrl+C ΡëαΜÉ dαΜΪng vΟ† quay lαΚΓi menu${RESET}"
    echo ""
    log "=== LOOP BαΚ°T ΡêαΚΠU | PlaceID=${PLACE_ID} | Pkg=${ROBLOX_PKG} ==="

    # LαΚßn ΡëαΚßu: mαΜü game ngay
    echo -e "${CYAN}[INIT] MαΜü Roblox game lαΚßn ΡëαΚßu...${RESET}"
    force_stop_and_rejoin
    echo -e "${CYAN}[INIT] ChαΜù ${DELAY_LOADING}s ΡëαΜÉ game tαΚΘi...${RESET}"
    sleep "$DELAY_LOADING"

    while true; do
        sleep "$DELAY_CHECK"
        local ts state elapsed
        ts=$(date '+%H:%M:%S')
        state=$(detect_state)
        elapsed=$(elapsed_since "$STATE_SINCE")

        # CαΚ≠p nhαΚ≠t thαΜùi ΡëiαΜÉm ΡëαΜïi trαΚΓng thΟΓi
        if [ "$state" != "$LAST_STATE" ]; then
            STATE_SINCE=$(now)
            elapsed=0
            log "TrαΚΓng thΟΓi ΡëαΜïi: ${LAST_STATE} βÜ£ ${state}"
        fi
        LAST_STATE="$state"

        case "$state" in

            GAME)
                # Ρêang chΤΓi game bΟ§nh thΤΑαΜùng
                FIRST_JOIN_DONE=true
                # LΤΑu lαΚΓi activity game ΡëαΜÉ phΟΓt hiαΜ΅n khi rαΜùi
                local act
                act=$(get_roblox_resumed_activity)
                [ -n "$act" ] && LAST_GAME_ACTIVITY="$act"
                echo -e "${GREEN}[${ts}] β€™ TRONG GAME | Rejoin: ${REJOIN_COUNT}x | Activity: ${act:-?}${RESET}"
                ;;

            LOADING)
                # Ρêang loading βÄî chαΜù, khΟ¥ng lΟ†m gΟ§
                echo -e "${CYAN}[${ts}] βè≥ LOADING... (${elapsed}s)${RESET}"
                # NαΚΩu loading quΟΓ lΟΔu (3 phΟΚt) thΟ§ force restart
                if [ "$elapsed" -gt 180 ]; then
                    echo -e "${RED}[${ts}] βö† Loading quΟΓ lΟΔu (${elapsed}s)! Force restart...${RESET}"
                    do_rejoin "Loading quΟΓ lΟΔu (${elapsed}s)"
                    force_stop_and_rejoin
                    echo -e "${CYAN}ChαΜù ${DELAY_LOADING}s...${RESET}"
                    sleep "$DELAY_LOADING"
                    STATE_SINCE=$(now)
                fi
                ;;

            HOME)
                # KαΚΙt αΜü Home Roblox βÄî chαΜù HOME_STUCK_TIMEOUT rαΜ™i gαΜ≠i lαΚΓi intent
                echo -e "${YELLOW}[${ts}] πüè† KαΚΗT HOME ROBLOX (${elapsed}s/${HOME_STUCK_TIMEOUT}s)${RESET}"
                if [ "$elapsed" -ge "$HOME_STUCK_TIMEOUT" ]; then
                    do_rejoin "KαΚΙt Home Roblox (${elapsed}s)"
                    echo -e "${CYAN}  βÜ£ GαΜ≠i lαΚΓi lαΜ΅nh vΟ†o game (khΟ¥ng kill)...${RESET}"
                    send_join_intent
                    echo -e "${CYAN}  βÜ£ ChαΜù ${DELAY_REJOIN}s...${RESET}"
                    sleep "$DELAY_REJOIN"
                    STATE_SINCE=$(now)
                    LAST_STATE=""

                    # NαΚΩu vαΚΪn cΟ≤n αΜü HOME sau khi gαΜ≠i intent 2 lαΚßn, force stop
                    sleep "$DELAY_CHECK"
                    local recheck
                    recheck=$(detect_state)
                    if [ "$recheck" = "HOME" ]; then
                        echo -e "${RED}  βÜ£ VαΚΪn kαΚΙt HOME! Force stop + rejoin...${RESET}"
                        log "VαΚΪn kαΚΙt HOME sau intent, force stop"
                        force_stop_and_rejoin
                        echo -e "${CYAN}  βÜ£ ChαΜù ${DELAY_LOADING}s...${RESET}"
                        sleep "$DELAY_LOADING"
                        STATE_SINCE=$(now)
                        LAST_STATE=""
                    fi
                fi
                ;;

            BLACK)
                # MΟ†n hΟ§nh Ρëen βÄî chαΜù BLACK_SCREEN_TIMEOUT rαΜ™i force restart
                echo -e "${RED}[${ts}] β§¦ MΟÄN HΟ¨NH ΡêEN/TREO (${elapsed}s/${BLACK_SCREEN_TIMEOUT}s)${RESET}"
                if [ "$elapsed" -ge "$BLACK_SCREEN_TIMEOUT" ]; then
                    do_rejoin "MΟ†n hΟ§nh Ρëen (${elapsed}s)"
                    echo -e "${RED}  βÜ£ Force stop + rejoin vΟ§ mΟ†n Ρëen quΟΓ lΟΔu...${RESET}"
                    log "MΟ†n Ρëen quΟΓ lΟΔu: force stop"
                    force_stop_and_rejoin
                    echo -e "${CYAN}  βÜ£ ChαΜù ${DELAY_LOADING}s...${RESET}"
                    sleep "$DELAY_LOADING"
                    STATE_SINCE=$(now)
                    LAST_STATE=""
                fi
                ;;

            DEAD)
                # Process Roblox chαΚΩt hoΟ†n toΟ†n
                echo -e "${RED}[${ts}] πü£Ä ROBLOX CHαΚΨT! Ρêang rejoin...${RESET}"
                do_rejoin "Process chαΚΩt"
                force_stop_and_rejoin
                echo -e "${CYAN}  βÜ£ ChαΜù ${DELAY_LOADING}s game tαΚΘi...${RESET}"
                sleep "$DELAY_LOADING"
                STATE_SINCE=$(now)
                LAST_STATE=""
                ;;

            BACKGROUND)
                # Roblox chαΚΓy nαΜ¹n, bαΜ΄ αΜ©ng dαΜΞng khΟΓc che
                echo -e "${BLUE}[${ts}] πü™≤ Roblox chαΚΓy nαΜ¹n (${elapsed}s)${RESET}"
                # ΡêΤΑa Roblox lΟΣn foreground
                if [ "$elapsed" -ge 10 ]; then
                    echo -e "${CYAN}  βÜ£ ΡêΤΑa Roblox lΟΣn foreground...${RESET}"
                    su -c "am start -p '${ROBLOX_PKG}'" > /dev/null 2>&1
                    sleep 3
                    STATE_SINCE=$(now)
                    LAST_STATE=""
                fi
                ;;

            *)
                echo -e "${YELLOW}[${ts}] ? TrαΚΓng thΟΓi khΟ¥ng xΟΓc ΡëαΜ΄nh: '${state}'${RESET}"
                ;;
        esac
    done

    IS_RUNNING=false
}

# βîÄβîÄβîÄ MENU CΟÄI ΡêαΚΕT βîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄβîÄ

